Date: 2001-09-28

Title: The Three-Dimensional Noncommutative Nonlinear Sigma Model in Superspace

Authors: H. O. Girotti, M. Gomes, A. Yu. Petrov, V. O. Rivelles and A. J. da

SilvaComments: 16 pages, 5 figures, Revtex

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B521 (2001) 119-126

We study the superspace formulation of the noncommutative nonlinearsupersymmetric O(N) invariant sigma-model in 2+1 dimensions. We prove that themodel is renormalizable to all orders of 1/N and explicitly verify that themodel is asymptotically free.